      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> have we benchmarked this?\n\nHi Alex,\n\nWe did not benchmark this on Lustre b2_5 branch because this patch was just back-ported to this branch. Cliff has been testing Lustre performance with ZFS back-end against Lustre 2.5.x releases. After this patch is landed, I think Cliff will get new performance data on Hyperion cluster while testing the upcoming Lustre 2.5.4 release.",
